95
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,653
Jangan pergi dulu!

96
00:06:02,737 --> 00:06:04,864
Kau tak mendengarku? Aku memperingatkanmu!

97
00:06:05,281 --> 00:06:06,449
Aku mendengarkanmu.

98
00:06:06,824 --> 00:06:09,160
- Apa lagi?
