99
00:06:09,327 --> 00:06:12,497
Monster itu awalnya
seorang seniman bela diri ternama.

100
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,623
Dia sungguh berbeda.

101
00:06:13,706 --> 00:06:15,166
Dia bisa menghancurkanmu.

102
00:06:15,958 --> 00:06:17,502
Jagoan seni bela diri?

103
00:06:17,585 --> 00:06:18,586
Bagus sekali.

104
00:06:18,669 --> 00:06:20,254
Lagi pula, aku masih belum puas.

105
00:06:21,631 --> 00:06:23,341
Hei, bukankah kau terluka?

106
00:06:23,674 --> 00:06:24,759
Jangan paksakan diri.

107
00:06:24,884 --> 00:06:26,260
Aku takkan membiarkanmu.

108
00:06:26,344 --> 00:06:29,055
Aku tak mau melihat penolongku ikut mati.

109
00:06:49,033 --> 00:06:50,701
Aku tak bisa menghentikannya!

110
00:06:55,289 --> 00:06:56,916
Tidak setiap hari

111
00:06:57,250 --> 00:07:00,253
