lebih banyak orang.

115
00:07:19,897 --> 00:07:21,065
Omong-omong,

116
00:07:21,149 --> 00:07:23,359
ada yang hampir lupa kuberi tahu padamu.

117
00:07:23,609 --> 00:07:26,279
Soal aku ikut turnamen sambil menyamar,

118
00:07:26,487 --> 00:07:27,989
