152
00:09:06,295 --> 00:09:08,214
Pelukan Malaikat!

153
00:09:15,221 --> 00:09:17,431
Dia mengawasi kita selama ini?

154
00:09:17,515 --> 00:09:18,557
Dia berlumuran darah.

155
00:09:20,434 --> 00:09:22,895
Halo, aku Puri-Puri Prisoner.

156
00:09:23,396 --> 00:09:24,355
Apa?

157
00:09:24,563 --> 00:09:27,858
Mereka mengambil semua sayangku
dari Sweet Garden?

158
00:09:29,068 --> 00:09:31,112
