Sepertinya alarmnya menyala,
tapi aku tak dengar apa pun.

186
00:10:55,112 --> 00:10:57,156
Kau tampak murung. Kau baik-baik saja?

187
00:10:57,490 --> 00:11:00,034
Aku memikirkan beberapa hal.

188
00:11:00,659 --> 00:11:01,660
Begitu rupanya.

189
00:11:01,869 --> 00:11:03,245
Tapi kau masih sangat muda.

190
00:11:03,329 --> 00:11:04,705
Kau tak boleh menyerah.

191
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,082
King...

192
